## 高级使用场景

### 1. 不同路径返回不同响应

使用多个 HTTPRoute 为不同路径配置不同的 mock 响应：

```yaml
# 用户列表 - 返回成功
---
apiVersion: gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: HTTPRoute
metadata:
  name: mock-users-list
spec:
  parentRefs:
    - name: my-gateway
  hostnames:
    - "api.example.com"
  rules:
    - matches:
        - path:
            type: Exact
            value: /api/users
          method: GET
      filters:
        - type: ExtensionRef
          extensionRef:
            group: edgion.io
            kind: EdgionPlugins
            name: mock-users-success
---
# 用户详情 - 返回 404
apiVersion: gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: HTTPRoute
metadata:
  name: mock-user-notfound
spec:
  parentRefs:
    - name: my-gateway
  hostnames:
    - "api.example.com"
  rules:
    - matches:
        - path:
            type: PathPrefix
            value: /api/users/999
      filters:
        - type: ExtensionRef
          extensionRef:
            group: edgion.io
            kind: EdgionPlugins
            name: mock-notfound
---
apiVersion: edgion.io/v1
kind: EdgionPlugins
metadata:
  name: mock-users-success
spec:
  plugins:
    - enable: true
      plugin:
        type: Mock
        config:
          statusCode: 200
          body: '{"users": [{"id": 1, "name": "Alice"}]}'
---
apiVersion: edgion.io/v1
kind: EdgionPlugins
metadata:
  name: mock-notfound
spec:
  plugins:
    - enable: true
      plugin:
        type: Mock
        config:
          statusCode: 404
          body: '{"error": "User not found"}'
```

