### 5. 开发环境：维护模式

在维护期间返回友好消息：

```yaml
filters:
  - type: Mock
    config:
      statusCode: 503
      contentType: "application/json"
      body: |
        {
          "status": "maintenance",
          "message": "System is under maintenance",
          "estimated_completion": "2024-03-15T10:00:00Z"
        }
      headers:
        Retry-After: "3600"
```

